videos.headline: Indiana's Ramsey escapes for 35-yard TD
videos.description: Peyton Ramsey jukes Maryland defenders for a 35-yard Indiana touchdown.

videos.headline: Indiana's Ramsey finds wide-open WR for TD
videos.description: Indiana's Peyton Ramsey is catching fire as he finds a wide-open Donavan Hale for a 37-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Indiana RB powers in 2-yard TD
videos.description: Indiana extends the lead as Stevie Scott powers up the middle for a 2-yard touchdown

videos.headline: Maryland RB walks in for 27-yard TD
videos.description: Maryland continues to chip away at Indiana's lead as Javon Leake goes untouched for a 27-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Maryland WR tip-toes on the sideline for 15-yard TD
videos.description: Maryland takes their first lead of the game as Tyrell Pigrome finds Jeshaun Jones who tip-toes on the sideline for a 15-yard touchdown
